# Development Workflow

## Available Scripts (from [package.json](mdc:package.json))

### Development
- `npm run dev` - Watch mode with tsx for rapid development
- `npm run build:watch` - TypeScript compilation in watch mode

### Production
- `npm run build` - TypeScript compilation
- `npm run start` - Production run with certificate validation
- `npm run start:unsafe` - Development run without cert validation (UNSAFE)

### Code Quality
- `npm run check` - Type check + lint
- `npm run types` - TypeScript type checking only
- `npm run lint` - Biome linting
- `npm run fix` - Auto-fix linting issues
- `npm run format` - Format code with Biome

## Environment Setup
- Use [utils/env.ts](mdc:utils/env.ts) for environment configuration
- Required: `OPENAI_API_KEY`
- Optional: `HTTPS_PROXY`, `PROXY_CERT_PATH`, `UNSAFE_PROXY`
- Development mode with `NODE_ENV=development`

## Proxy Configuration
- [utils/proxy.ts](mdc:utils/proxy.ts) handles proxy setup
- Secure mode: Uses certificate validation (default)
- Unsafe mode: Disables certificate validation (development only)
- Certificate path: `./ca.pem` (configurable via `PROXY_CERT_PATH`)
